# 🌍 Climate XAI Predictor

An explainable AI frontend for climate variable forecasting. Predicts **Temperature**, **Rainfall**, and **CO₂** levels from environmental inputs, with full **SHAP-style feature contribution** visualizations per prediction.

---

## ✨ Features

- **3 Predictions** — Temperature (°C), Rainfall (mm), CO₂ (ppm)
- **SHAP Explanations** — Horizontal bar charts showing each feature's contribution to each prediction
- **Absolute / Percentage Mode** — Toggle between raw contribution values and normalized percentages
- **Scenario Manager** — Save, load, and delete named input+result snapshots (persisted in localStorage)
- **Compare Mode** — Run two predictions and see delta values side-by-side on cards
- **Export** — Download results as PNG screenshot or JSON data file
- **Model Info Sidebar** — R² accuracy metrics, algorithm details, training metadata
- **Demo Mode** — Fully functional with realistic mock data, no backend required
- **Responsive** — Works on desktop, tablet, and mobile
- **Accessible** — WCAG 2.1 AA: keyboard nav, ARIA labels, focus styles, reduced-motion support

