## 🔌 Backend API Contract

### `POST /api/predict`

**Request body:**
```json
{
  "wind_speed": 4.2,
  "humidity": 65,
  "atmospheric_pressure": 1013.25,
  "solar_radiation": 220,
  "cloud_cover": 35,
  "precipitation_lag": 6.5,
  "temperature_lag": 22.0,
  "co2_lag": 415.3
}
```

**Expected response:**
```json
{
  "predictions": {
    "temperature": 25.6,
    "rainfall": 12.3,
    "co2": 415.7
  },
  "explanations": {
    "temperature": [
      { "feature": "wind_speed", "contribution": -0.84, "label": "Wind Speed" },
      { "feature": "solar_radiation", "contribution": 3.96, "label": "Solar Radiation" }
    ],
    "rainfall": [ ... ],
    "co2": [ ... ]
  },
  "model_info": {
    "version": "v2.1.4",
    "training_date": "2024-11-15",
    "r2_temperature": 0.923,
    "r2_rainfall": 0.871,
    "r2_co2": 0.988,
    "algorithm": "Gradient Boosted Trees (XGBoost)"
  }
}
```

- `contribution` — SHAP value (positive = pushes prediction up, negative = pushes down)
- `label` — Human-readable feature name for display
- `model_info` — Optional; shown in the Model Info sidebar if present

