## 🧩 Input Features

| Key | Label | Unit | Range |
|-----|-------|------|-------|
| `wind_speed` | Wind Speed | m/s | 0 – 120 |
| `humidity` | Humidity | % | 0 – 100 |
| `atmospheric_pressure` | Atmospheric Pressure | hPa | 870 – 1085 |
| `solar_radiation` | Solar Radiation | W/m² | 0 – 1400 |
| `cloud_cover` | Cloud Cover | % | 0 – 100 |
| `precipitation_lag` | Precipitation (lag) | mm | 0 – 500 |
| `temperature_lag` | Temperature (lag) | °C | -60 – 60 |
| `co2_lag` | CO₂ (lag) | ppm | 280 – 600 |

To add or remove features, update `FEATURE_RANGES` in `src/context/store.js`.  
The form generates input fields dynamically from that config object.

